Megan Walsch (Hailee Steinfeld) is een 16-jarig meisje dat is opgegroeid

Storyline

Megan Walsh has been training to be an international assassin for Hardman.
However while she is on a mission, she notices how other teenagers her age
seem to be having fun and enjoying their lives. Desiring a normal life, she
bails out of a mission and enrolls in a student exchange program, in the
process, being adopted by a foster family. She soon becomes a part of the
high school and is subjected to the pressures and life of being in this
environment.
